Builds teal_card from code and outputs in qenv object

Source: R/teal_card.R
dot-code_to_card.Rd

Builds a teal_card from the code and outputs of a teal_data object, preserving the order of code execution and output display.

Usage 

.code_to_card(x, code_block_opts = list())

Arguments

x

(list) object from qenv@code.

code_block_opts

(list) Additional options for the R code chunk in R Markdown.

Value

A teal_card built from the code and outputs in a qenv object.

On this page

teal.reporter is a part of the NEST and pharmaverse.
